	<h3 id="theme3">Problems and Bugs</h3>
	<div class="k-panel">
		<h4 class="control"><a href="#" title="Click to fold/unfold block">I can't copy the HTML (CSS/JS) code. What is happenning?</a></h4>
		<div class="content k-article">
			<p>In the Kawwa Portal we use ZeroClipboard to the copy/paste feature.</p>
			<p>ZeroClipboard is a quite reliable function that relies on the flash "swf" format to control some browser security issues. So, if you're facing problems copying code, 
			please check if you have the Flash Player on your browser.</p>  
			<p>If you do, we suggest you reload the page and try again. If you face this problem often, please let us know. You may send us a message precising 
			your problem to our distribution list at <a href="mailto:dl-kawwa@atos.net">dl-kawwa@atos.net</a>.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

